sentences: Ta võtab omavahel vastu suhtleb inimestega.
Need kaks inimest on omavahel väga sarnased.
Nende kahe inimese vahel on omavahel suur sõprus.
context: The word 'omavahel' is used in Estonian to describe a mutual or reciprocal relationship between two or more people or things, indicating that they are interacting or connected with each other.
